ï»¿[ActionMessage_ONS]
; EN: Messages[0]="Welcome to Onslaught Training."
Messages[0]="Benvingut a l'entrenament Onslaught."
; EN: Messages[1]="There are many types of vehicles."
Messages[1]="Hi ha molts tipus de vehicles."
; EN: Messages[2]="The 'USE' key gets in or out of vehicles."
Messages[2]="La clau 'USE' entra o surt dels vehicles."
; EN: Messages[3]="Some vehicles can hold passengers."
Messages[3]="Alguns vehicles poden contenir passatgers."
; EN: Messages[4]="Each team in Onslaught has a PowerCore."
Messages[4]="Cada equip d'Onslaught tĂ© un PowerCore."
; EN: Messages[5]="PowerCores are connected to each other through PowerNodes."
Messages[5]="Els PowerCores es connecten entre ells mitjanĂ§ant PowerNodes."
; EN: Messages[6]="You can see the network of PowerNodes in the overhead map."
Messages[6]="Podeu veure la xarxa de PowerNodes al mapa general."
; EN: Messages[7]="The objective is to destroy the other team's PowerCore."
Messages[7]="L'objectiu Ă©s destruir el PowerCore de l'altre equip."
; EN: Messages[8]="You may only attack Nodes and Cores which are linked to a Node or Core you already control."
Messages[8]="NomĂ©s podeu atacar nodes i nuclis que estiguin vinculats a un node o nucli que ja controleu."
; EN: Messages[9]="To take a PowerNode, destroy it if it is controlled by the enemy."
Messages[9]="Per agafar un PowerNode, destrueix-lo si estĂ  controlat per l'enemic."
; EN: Messages[10]="Touch a neutral PowerAccessPoint to create a friendly PowerNode."
Messages[10]="Toqueu un PowerAccessPoint neutre per crear un PowerNode amigable."
; EN: Messages[11]="Vehicles appear near friendly Nodes and your Core."
Messages[11]="Els vehicles apareixen a prop dels Nodes amics i del vostre Core."
; EN: Messages[12]="Until moved, vehicles are locked against the enemy team."
Messages[12]="Fins que no es mouen, els vehicles estan bloquejats contra l'equip enemic."
; EN: Messages[13]="The Link Gun can heal vehicles and Nodes."
Messages[13]="La pistola d'enllaĂ§ pot curar vehicles i nodes."
; EN: Messages[14]="Damaged PowerCores can NOT be healed."
Messages[14]="Els Powercore danyats NO es poden curar."
; EN: Messages[15]="Build a network of Nodes to gain access to the enemy Core,"
Messages[15]="Construeix una xarxa de nodes per accedir al nucli enemic,"
; EN: Messages[16]="then destroy it."
Messages[16]="desprĂ©s destrueix-lo."
; EN: Messages[17]="This concludes the Onslaught Tutorial. Good luck."
Messages[17]="AixĂ² conclou el Tutorial d'Onslaught. Bona sort."

